PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Adele MacDonald, Sydney, Nova Scotia, in the place of Selma Rudderham, whose term has expired; and Michael MacDonald, Sydney, Nova Scotia, in the place of David MacDonald, whose term has expired)
